/-- `Kernel.pow κ n` is the `n`-fold composition of the kernel `κ`, with `pow κ 0 = id`. -/
noncomputable def pow {α : Type*} [MeasurableSpace α] (κ : Kernel α α) : ℕ → Kernel α α
| 0     => Kernel.id
| n + 1 => κ ∘ₖ (pow κ n)

